{"tid":252022,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《極道鮮師》仲間由紀惠剪短髮！身材腫2倍大網友崩潰","createTime":"2017-05-21T11:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T11:43:33.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0de48a2facbe5fbe32861bdf5b6a245332ce93b","tid":252022,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2537/d2537052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2537%2Fd2537052.jpg&h=209705e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲仲間由紀惠1月出席記者會時，身材發腫（右）成為話題。<br />\n<br />\n日本女星仲間由紀惠因《極道鮮師》爆紅，出道以來都是長髮示人，近日主持音樂節目《MUSIC FAIR》，以短髮造型亮相震撼網路。她的黑色長髮被削短變出層次，前額修剪出厚劉海，令大批網友直呼不自然，再加上身材變腫，令人悲喊「變大Size了！」<br />\n<br />\n仲間由紀惠1月出席電視劇記者會時，身穿紅色無袖洋裝，身材圓潤豐滿，一度傳出疑似懷孕。有雜誌爆料，她和演員老公田中哲司結婚3年，BTOB恩光脫了！陸星材盯著6塊腹肌感嘆：哇～豐富最近正在準備懷孕，為此減少工作，連春季日劇《貴族偵探》都只以聲音演出，難得主持音樂節目，卻再度令觀眾驚呼「變胖了」、「結婚太幸福了嗎？」有部分網友推測，身材發福可能與生子計畫有關。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2537/d2537050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2537%2Fd2537050.jpg&h=62b2029c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲仲間由紀惠主持音樂節目，首度將招牌長髮剪短！<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2537/d2537049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2537%2Fd2537049.jpg&h=6a860df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲仲間由紀惠剪短髮加上身材變腫，網友悲喊外型劣化。<br />\n<br />\n現年37歲的仲間由紀惠除了甜美臉蛋，演技精湛更是擄獲男女粉絲的心，黑色直長髮已經是招牌造型。她首次改變髮型，網友哀聲連連，眾人輪番感嘆「髮型不適合」、「雖然還是很美，但是體型真的很難維持了」、「這好像假髮」、「再次確認造型真的很重要。」"},{"pid":"bb9d05de811bc65c2e0240278dc53160a6b7e81f","tid":252022,"uid":84998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"下圖似47定57歲"},{"pid":"91ac8ad1710a71415bb9f10a60e1c50589f3c16e","tid":252022,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:04:01.000Z","msg":"老啦，睇佢個陣我小學，依家都就快大學畢業<br />\n唔係咁多個林志玲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74d0e4223a5c87bb32e0257ba677557388f37da","tid":252022,"uid":29898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"歲月不留人<br />\nBtw<br />\n佢扮老師個look真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d321f6ee66a33bcc056e66071ce8925b552617ed","tid":252022,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:30:01.000Z","msg":"其實成日話日本啲styling、fashion有幾好<br />\n點解啲藝人次次剪髮都炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ecabc904273b8e9e38a5d508723a345901fdc0","tid":252022,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"極道鮮師好睇"},{"pid":"8af65bf21d3c43be0a1f5080e06a251fe56433d2","tid":252022,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/k65342005/1187739839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fk65342005%2F1187739839.jpg&h=b6d8c35c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f18fb83cfd8a61c0db8b1e78ee5ca9b9eceaedb","tid":252022,"uid":66048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"其實都肥咗一段時間啦，一結完婚就肥咗好多，可能幸福肥掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實今次最大獲都係個髮型啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆佢個街，都唔知邊條友咁撚弱智將佢個頭剪成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}